        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting Consumers from PFAS Act</b></p> <p>This bill adds the Consumer Product Safety Commission to the interagency working group to coordinate federal activities related to research about perfluoroalkyl or polyfluoroalkyl substances, commonly referred to as PFAS.</p>]]></text>
